HEADWORD: Joe-Pye weed
<hw>Joe`-Pye" weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A tall
composite plant of the genus <gen>Eupatorium</gen> (<spn>Eupatorium
purpureum</spn>), with purplish flowers, and whorled leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
